Q: 24/7 Jet Inc.在2024年哪个月份的飞行量最大？该月的总航班数量是多少？
SQL:
SELECT
        a.date_month,
        count(*) as num
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
        b.supplier_id = "1001"
        AND a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
        AND '2024-12'
GROUP BY
        a.date_month
ORDER BY
        num DESC
        LIMIT 1;

        count(*) as num
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
        b.supplier_id = "1064"
        AND a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
        AND '2024-12'
GROUP BY
        a.date_month
ORDER BY
        num DESC
        LIMIT 1;
